{"id":"guide/doc-tasks","title":"Overview of documentation maintenance tasks","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/doc-tasks.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"overview-of-documentation-maintenance-tasks\" translation-result=\"on\">文件維護任務概覽<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/doc-tasks#overview-of-documentation-maintenance-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Overview of documentation maintenance tasks<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/doc-tasks#overview-of-documentation-maintenance-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 文件需要日常維護以保持最新。本節中的主題描述了你可以執行的日常維護任務，以幫助使 Angular 文件保持良好狀態。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The Angular documentation needs routine maintenance to keep it up-to-date.\nThe topics in this section describe routine maintenance tasks that you can perform to help keep the Angular documentation in good condition.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">文件維護任務分為以下兩類：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Documentation maintenance tasks fall into these two categories:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">細微的變化</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Minor changes</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">主要變化</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Major changes</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">可以在 GitHub 站點中進行小的更改，而無需在你的系統上載入任何軟體或工具。有關對文件進行次要更改的資訊，請參閱<a href=\"guide/contributors-guide-overview#make-a-minor-change\">進行次要更改</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Minor changes can be made in the GitHub site without the need to load any software or tools on your system.\nFor information about making a minor change to the documentation, see <a href=\"guide/contributors-guide-overview#make-a-minor-change\">Make a minor change</a>.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">重大更改要求你在將更改傳送到 Angular 文件之前，在本地計算機上建構和測試對文件的更改。有關準備你的系統以對文件進行重大更改的資訊，請參閱<a href=\"guide/contributors-guide-overview#make-a-major-change\">進行重大更改</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Major changes require that you build and test your changes to the documentation on your local computer before you send them to the Angular documentation.\nFor information about preparing your system to make major changes to the documentation, see <a href=\"guide/contributors-guide-overview#make-a-major-change\">Make a major change</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"routine-documentation-maintenance-tasks\" translation-result=\"on\">日常文件維護任務<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/doc-tasks#routine-documentation-maintenance-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Routine documentation maintenance tasks<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/doc-tasks#routine-documentation-maintenance-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">任務</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Task</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">範圍</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Scope</nt-wrapper></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/reviewing-content\">檢視當前文件</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/reviewing-content\">Review current documentation</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">次要（見注）</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Minor (See note)</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/updating-search-keywords\">更新搜尋關鍵字</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/updating-search-keywords\">Update search keywords</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">次要</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Minor</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/docs-lint-errors\">解決 linter 錯誤</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/docs-lint-errors\">Resolve linter errors</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">專業</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Major</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/doc-select-issue\">解決文件問題</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/doc-select-issue\">Resolve documentation issues</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">專業</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Major</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: <br>\nReviewing current documentation requires a minor change if all you need to do is update the <code>@reviewed</code>   date.\nIf you find a minor problem with a documentation topic, such as a typo, fixing it during your review is also a minor change.</p>\n<p>If you find an issue that you don't feel comfortable fixing, <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/new?assignees=&amp;labels=&amp;template=3-docs-bug.yaml\">open a docs issue</a> in GitHub so someone else can fix it.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：10/12/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/contributors-guide-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/contributors-guide-overview#make-a-major-change\n - guide/contributors-guide-overview#make-a-minor-change\n - guide/doc-select-issue\n - guide/doc-tasks#overview-of-documentation-maintenance-tasks\n - guide/doc-tasks#routine-documentation-maintenance-tasks\n - guide/doc-tasks#文件維護任務概覽\n - guide/doc-tasks#日常文件維護任務\n - guide/docs-lint-errors\n - guide/reviewing-content\n - guide/updating-search-keywords\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/new?assignees=&labels=&template=3-docs-bug.yaml\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/doc-tasks.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}